description: Jack went over to Jay's house to help him wash his parent's car. It was a hot day and they ended up quickly washing and rushing into the AC. Jack had no idea what his friend, Jay, had planned for him. Jay had wanted Jack since he first met him, 2 years ago. Jack is straight tho, so Jay was only dreaming---over time, however, he sensed Jack might be nudged into experimenting with a dude. So Jay decided to go for it, and, to his happy surprise, Jack was willing! And, the straight dude took it up his virgin ass!
title: Jizzy Jay
